Package: sounDMR
Title: DMR analysis from ONT data for aws batch operations
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Tom", "Cairns", email = "t.cairns@sound.ag", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Jack", "Colicchio", email = "j.colicchio@sound.ag", role = "aut"),
    person("Michael", "Flashman", email = "m.flashman@sound.ag", role = "aut"),
    person("Keerthana", "Prabhu", email = "k.prabhu@sound.ag", role = "aut"))
Description: This package provides robust functions for DMR analysis. It takes in a megaframe,
             cleans with the help of the programmer, then runs the random effects model for a
             given formula, and finally identifies the changepoints in the Z score of interest from
             the random effects model.
